  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to collect plasma, serum, whole blood and tissue samples from
      women with breast cancer and plasma, serum, whole blood from healthy women, which will be
      made available to researchers for biomarker analysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      OUTLINE: This is a multi-center study.

      The treatment plan for each breast cancer subject will be determined at the discretion of the
      treating physician and subject. This protocol does not prescribe any particular standard of
      care treatment.

      There will be no treatment for the healthy volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
